{"tid":2141845,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"維族少年被囚 拍片爆教育營慘況","createTime":"2020-08-06T04:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T04:37:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1197c0501d4b268f7d9372e4cd18637355902e7b","tid":2141845,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:18:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200806/AB3RFFSU4EKXSJEF366R4C7XUI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200806%2FAB3RFFSU4EKXSJEF366R4C7XUI%2F&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F1RUXPbyrNnFnNFpNAJjDn8%3D&h=10f78fb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200806%2FAB3RFFSU4EKXSJEF366R4C7XUI%2F&h=e6dd62bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200806/AB3RFFSU4EKXSJEF366R4C7XUI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n維族少年被囚 拍片爆教育營慘況<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JXRgT1D6bTH-qN7zJtFYeAFybsU=/640x489/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WUZTBHEL7RV2CMNCFUZPLDAGVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJXRgT1D6bTH-qN7zJtFYeAFybsU%3D%2F640x489%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWUZTBHEL7RV2CMNCFUZPLDAGVU.jpg&h=b2b75ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司（BBC）刊出一段聲稱來自新疆「再教育營」囚禁者發放的片段及文字，片中可見拍片者被關在一間房，一隻手被鎖在床上（圖）。片中人更聲稱見到有四名青年在囚禁期間被「打至不能坐」。BBC 引述專家稱片中情況可信，再次炒熱中國人權問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱目擊青年遭毒打<br />\n<br />\n拍片者是維族人Merdan Ghappar ，。。。。。。。。。。，不料隨即遭送入「再教育營」。<br />\n<br />\n根據BBC 的報道，Ghappar因有感冒症狀，被送到流行病控制中心，才能以手機拍下房間及對外通訊。根據片段，他的手被手銬鎖在鐵架床上，另一隻手拍攝房間的黃色大門及鐵窗。<br />\n<br />\nGhappar的微信文字則記錄在新疆被扣查情況。他指自己看到50至60人關在面積不到500平方呎的小房子，然後被迫戴帶「四件套」，即「黑色布頭套、手銬、腳鏈及手銬腳鏈之間的鐵鏈。」。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。BBC 稱未能確認片中的地點，但引述新疆專家稱片段中聽到房間外有廣播指「新疆從來不是東突厥斯坦」，認為影片真實性高。該新聞在英國瘋傳，不少英國政要甚為關注，Ghappar已有數月音訊全無。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司"},{"pid":"17b4fe9f41a66680b79ae91727a4ac9f981caf32","tid":2141845,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:37:08.000Z","msg":"大好青年被囚禁，虛耗青春，肉體受酷刑，甚至永久殘費，要幾無人性既人至會對極權政府獻眉、趨之若鶩？"}]}